name: Blog News IOS App Figma & PSD Template
description:
Blog News IOS App Figma & PSD Template

Modern iOS User Interface design template for a Blog / News app. This template is ideal for a blog app, media online, news app, and any media app. Make your wallet app design looks stunning and eye-catching using this template. This template includes 12 unique and modern User Interface screens in PSD and Figma format. You can edit and customize easily using Adobe Photoshop and Figma.

Highlights:

+ 12 High-quality Screens in PSD and Figma Template

+ Designed for Blog and News app

+ Using FREE Font from Google Font

+ Well Documented

+ Easy to edit and customize

+ using 375px x 812px, recommended size for iPhone XI Pro
